{"tid":1328310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入境處：每日有300名新移民並非事實","createTime":"2019-07-18T01:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:12:05.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":666,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"180c2e30e2bd9448d4e6711de5913106242aa6b4","tid":1328310,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"對於近日網上指每日預留150個單程證和150個專才配額，入境處澄清沒有相關安排。<br />\n<br />\n對於網上傳言指本港每日有300名新移民轉為永久居民一事，入境處表示，該項安排只為便利一些剛獲批居留權的市民，由於他們已按預約時間到辦事處辦理領取居留權的手續，為免他們另行安排再次到辦事處，辦理換領永久性居民身份證的手續，安排他們在領取完居留權後，可選擇即時到辦事處的人事登記處辦理相關手續。<br />\n<br />\n入境處重申，有關安排不會對其他居民正常辦理其身份證手續造成任何影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2194228/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2194228%2F&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=e5413363\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2194228/</a>"},{"pid":"e9a63ce52523daa344639ded1b078b727acfeffd","tid":1328310,"uid":60434,"like":504,"dislike":1,"score":503,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"唔止300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e035cc5b264e59b6c7030a8b2b176306cd1b88","tid":1328310,"uid":18639,"like":562,"dislike":1,"score":561,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"入境處：事實係多過300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a7e7670d437bec849bb5c8c6a800a95e3752ab","tid":1328310,"uid":32749,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c0c6b5c259307644ccb0ce1ab2ae2fcd81635e","tid":1328310,"uid":186509,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feb98c9ec9026fe7ba334c2c6a4beaa3d9c13f87","tid":1328310,"uid":70336